Use case label: UC09.01.03
Use Story: US09.01.03
Test case: testCacheOffline() in testOffline.java
Participating actor: Borrower
Goal :  Be able to cache the inventories of the friends that has been previous looked at and browse them while offline.
Tigger : Borrower's device is currently offline and try to browse in the inventories of his friends which he previous looked at.
Precondition: Borrower clicked into one of his friends' inventory while offline
Postcondition: Inventory is showed to the borrower
Basic Flow:
    Borrower proposed a new trade with a selected friend
    System saves the trade locally
    System pushes trade online once it connects to the internet
